             were indicted for <rs id="t17790113-7-off35" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17790113-7-off35" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17790113-7-off35" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing seven pair of silk stockings, value 4 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17790113-7-victim106" type="victimName">
                     John
                      Thorold Darvin
                  <interp inst="t17790113-7-victim106" type="surname" value="Thorold Darvin"></interp>
